Deploy directly using the Netlify CLI
When correcting some small bug, do only edit part of the code only that is needed
When making a feature, sure to preserve all features. Do not overwrite everything.
When fixing a bug, correct the bug but make sure to preserve all features. Do not overwrite everything.
Do not deploy to Netlify if not requested
Always try first to apply a simpler approach to fix issues by focusing only on the specific problem